Support
Conjurer's Pursuit;;1;Every 3 Regeneration Globes gathered grants an extra +0.25 Mana per second, permanently.
Reach;;1;Holy Light range increased by 2.
Dense Weightstone;;1;Hammer of Justice damage increased by 40%.
Blessed Champion;;1;Basic Attacks heal nearby allies for 25% of the damage dealt.
Hammer of the Lightbringer;;4;Basic Attacks also restore 5 Mana.
Fist of Justice;;4;Basic Attacks reduce cooldown of Hammer of Justice by 1 second.
Protect the Weak;;4;Using Holy Light on Minions and Mercenaries refunds -24% of its Mana cost and cooldown.
Protective Shield;;4;Activate to shield an allied Hero from 300 damage for 5 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Wave of Light;;7;Each unit healed by Holy Radiance returns 10 Mana and reduces the cooldown by 1 second, up to a maximum of 50 Mana and 5 seconds.
Rebuke;;7;Hammer of Justice knocks the target back.
Holy Devotion (Trait);;7;Damage and healing have 100% effectiveness while in Spirit Form.
Clairvoyance;;7;Activate to reveal the target area. Enemies in the area are revealed for 4 seconds. 45s cooldown.
Cleanse;;7;Activate to remove all stuns, roots, silences, and slows from the target and prevents their reapplication for 1 second. 30s cooldown.
Divine Shield;;10;Make an allied Hero Invulnerable and increase their Movement Speed by 20% for 3 seconds. 90s cooldown.
Divine Storm;;10;Deal 75 damage and stun nearby enemies for 1.5 seconds. 70s cooldown.
Burning Rage;;13;Deal 10 damage per second to nearby enemies.
Spell Shield;;13;Upon taking Ability Damage, reduce all Ability Damage taken by 50% for 2 seconds. Can only trigger once every 30 seconds.
Sprint;;13;Activate to gain 75% Movement Speed for 3 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Shrink Ray;;13;Activate to reduce an enemy Hero's damage by 50% and Movement Speed by 50% for 4 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Hardened Focus;;16;While above 80% life, your Basic Ability cooldowns regenerate 50% faster.
Gathering Radiance;;16;Increases damage and healing by 10% for each target hit, up to 50%.
Holy Shock;;16;Holy Light can be used on an enemy to do 50% of its healing amount as damage.
Imposing Presence;;16;Enemies that attack you have their Attack Speed slowed by 30%.
Resurgence of the Storm;;20;Upon dying, revive back at your Altar after 5 seconds. This can occur once every 120 seconds.
Storm Shield;;20;Activate to give all nearby allied Heroes a Shield for 20% of their max Health for 3 seconds. 45s cooldown.
Bulwark of Light;;20;Divine Shield lasts 1 second longer and Uther also gains Divine Shield on cast.
Divine Hurricane;;20;Divine Storm's radius is increased by 100% and its cooldown is reduced by 20 seconds.